1013
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:05,900
 Isus kaže,

1014
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:07,100
 šta joj dosađujete?

1015
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:08,740
 Dobro je djelo učinila.

1016
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:10,440
 Što je mogla učinila,

1017
00:38:10,440 --> 00:38:11,140
 počastila?

1018
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:11,840
 Isus je znao

1019
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,180
 da ona

1020
00:38:12,180 --> 00:38:13,800
 časteći njega

1021
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,520
 časti oca.

1022
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,840
 I pazite kako je

1023
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:17,020
 nagradu odmah dao.

1024
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:18,440
 kaže,

1025
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,380
 gdje god se bude

1026
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:20,540
 pričalo o ovo evanđelje,

1027
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:22,220
 govorit će se

1028
00:38:22,220 --> 00:38:23,340
 što je ova žena učinila.

1029
00:38:23,340 --> 00:38:24,840
 I mi danas znamo,

1030
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:26,480
 Marija Magdalena je to učinila.

1031
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,280
 Kakvu časti ima

1032
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,160
 onaj farizej,

1033
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:30,960
 kojeg ne znaš kak se zove,

1034
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,820
 nego je farizej,

1035
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:32,480
 pismo znanac.

1036
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,620
 To je tako ružan pojam.

1037
00:38:33,620 --> 00:38:35,860
 A ime ostali su

1038
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:36,660
 zapomčili imena

1039
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,900
 samo onih zloglasnih.

1040
00:38:37,900 --> 00:38:39,160
 Pilat,

1041
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:39,860
 po čemu je znao?

1042
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:41,980
 Samo po negativnom događaju

1043
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:42,500
 koju činio.

1044
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:43,420
 kajfa.

1045
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:50,340
 Sveti Franjo,

1046
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:51,780
 Salešk je slično stvar,

1047
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,060
 rekao,

1048
00:38:52,060 --> 00:38:53,680
 svatite gdje ste posađeni.

1049
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:58,240
 Naravno da se sad pitate

1050
00:38:58,240 --> 00:38:59,460
 šta ako ti,

1051
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:01,740
 naši crkveni autoriteti,

1052
00:39:01,740 --> 00:39:05,420
 su pokvareni.

1053
00:39:05,420 --> 00:39:07,400
 Šta ako taj svećenik,

1054
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,300
 šta ako taj vojitelj,

1055
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:10,000
 zajedni sa stvarima krive motive,

1056
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,900
 i ako čini zlo.

1057
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,060
 Jel to znači

1058
00:39:14,060 --> 00:39:15,680
 da ga ja trebam častiti?

1059
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:16,600
 Ja vam kažem da.

1060
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:19,300
 Evo pogledajte primjer

1061
00:39:19,300 --> 00:39:21,140
 Ane i Elija.

1062
00:39:21,140 --> 00:39:23,640
 Ana je majka Samuelova,

1063
00:39:23,640 --> 00:39:24,820
 nije mogla dobiti djete.

1064
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:26,620
 I bila je u muci,

1065
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:27,140
 jer joj se

1066
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:29,840
 druga žena njenog muža

1067
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:31,700
 toliko joj se rugala,

1068
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,300
 toliko joj ponižavala

1069
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:34,440
 zbog toga što ona ne može

1070
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:34,960
 dobiti djete,

1071
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:36,360
 da je bila jadna i nikakva.

1072
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:38,940
 I kada je došla u hram,

1073
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:41,020
 odnosno u hram,

1074
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:43,120
 kad su prinosili žrtve,

1075
00:39:43,120 --> 00:39:45,300
 Elija je tad bio svećenik,

1076
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:46,240
 veliki svećenik,

1077
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,480
 koji je bio pokvaren lik.

1078
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,280
 Pustio da njegovi sinovi

1079
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:52,460
 bludniče sa hramskim djevojkama,

1080
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:54,400
 koje su čuvale šator.

1081
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:57,640
 Pustio ih je da kradu od žrtava

1082
00:39:57,640 --> 00:40:00,840
 koje su ljudi prinosili Bogu.

1083
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:02,140
 Jer mu je pasalo,

1084
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:03,200
 jer je on dobio dio.

1085
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:06,060
 I ona je plakala, ridala,

1086
00:40:06,060 --> 00:40:07,980
 molila Boga

1087
00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:09,640
 i šapčeći

1088
00:40:09,640 --> 00:40:12,200
 prikazivala svoju molitvu.

1089
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,600
 I kad je to vidio Eli,

1090
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:13,960
 rekao je,

1091
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:14,680
 šta si pijan?

1092
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:15,740
 Ajde, otrezni se više.

1093
00:40:15,740 --> 00:40:17,840
 Zamislite da danas vi dođete

1094
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:18,840
 u tu situaciju,

1095
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:19,840
 dođem svećenik,

1096
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:20,320
 ili bojite,

1097
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:21,180
 šta si pijan?

1098
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:22,500
 A ti izljevaš dušu.

1099
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:23,620
 Pa poludili bi,

1100
00:40:23,620 --> 00:40:24,500
 idem u drugu crku,

1101
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:25,780
 neće ti tu više nikad doći.

1102
00:40:25,780 --> 00:40:29,900
 Kakav si ti to svećenik?

1103
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,280
 T, t, t, t, t, t, t, t, t.

1104
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,880
 A šta mu ona rekla?

1105
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:33,620
 Gospodaru.

1106
00:40:33,620 --> 00:40:36,380
 Jadna sam i nevoljna

1107
00:40:36,380 --> 00:40:37,200
 i tako dalje.

1108
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:39,540
 Ne sudi me krivo,

1109
00:40:39,540 --> 00:40:40,400
 ali gospodaru.

1110
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:43,900
 I šta je on kaže?

1111
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,900
 Dobro, nek ti Jahve usliši.

1112
00:40:48,660 --> 00:40:49,360
 Ona ga je častila,

1113
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,560
 ne zato što je bio pokvarin

1114
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,780
 i zato što je bio svet.

1115
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,340
 Nije bio ni svet,

1116
00:40:54,340 --> 00:40:56,260
 niti joj dobro pristupio,

1117
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:58,120
 ali ga je počastila.

1118
00:40:58,120 --> 00:40:59,880
 Jel je bio duhovni autoritet.

1119
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,580
 I molitve su uslišane.

1120
00:41:01,580 --> 00:41:04,040
 Možeš bolji primjer Davida

1121
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,680
 i Šaula.

1122
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:09,260
 Kad je neko bio pomazan

1123
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:09,920
 tad za kralja,

1124
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,640
 on je imao vlast veliku.

1125
00:41:11,640 --> 00:41:16,180
 I David,

1126
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:20,520
 kako je rastao,

1127
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:21,480
 rastao svetosti,

1128
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,760
 vježbao svoj gospodinu,

1129
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,440
 postoje,

1130
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,640
 oslobodio je,

1131
00:41:24,640 --> 00:41:25,220
 imao je onu

1132
00:41:25,220 --> 00:41:28,100
 zgodu sa Filistejcem,

1133
00:41:28,100 --> 00:41:29,960
 počeo je ići u ratne pohode

1134
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:30,880
 i bio jako uspješan.

1135
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,660
 Onda su djevojke,

1136
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:32,340
 žene pjevale,

1137
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:33,740
 Šaul pobi tisuće,

1138
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:35,080
 David desetke tisuća.

1139
00:41:35,080 --> 00:41:36,720
 I Šaulu se to nije svidilo,

1140
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,600
 ali on je bio kralj.

1141
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,960
 I pobojao se za svoje kraljevstvo,

1142
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:41,980
 da će mu David preuzeti.

1143
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:44,940
 Zavist ušla u njegov srce,

1144
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:46,200
 mržnja

1145
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:48,140
 i želja da ga ubije.

1146
00:41:48,140 --> 00:41:51,080
 Dva put je pokušao ga ubijet dok mu je sviro

1147
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:53,560
 i treći put

1148
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:56,020
 kad je pozvao na gozbu,

1149
00:41:56,020 --> 00:41:57,960
 onda je David to prepozno,

1150
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:00,520
 Jonathan mu javio da ga ovaj stvarno želi ubiti

1151
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:02,660
 i David odlazi u bijeg.

1152
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:06,280
 Njemu se priključuju svi nesvrstani,

1153
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:10,100
 svi koji nisu zadovoljni,

1154
00:42:10,100 --> 00:42:12,160
 pljačkaši i sl.

1155
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:16,160
 I on postaje njihov vođa.

1156
00:42:16,160 --> 00:42:20,840
 I Šaul iznova, iznova pokušao obijet Davida.

1157
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:24,060
 I jedne prilike da ga lovia po tim špiljama,

1158
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:26,820
 oni su se sakrali u jednu duboku špilju,

1159
00:42:26,820 --> 00:42:30,540
 a kaže sve to pismo da je Šaul došao čučnut.

1160
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:36,560
 Što znači došao je obavit fiziološke potrebe.

1161
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:39,080
 I dok je on to radio,

1162
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:40,820
 rekli su Davidovi,

1163
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:42,500
 sad ti je Bog dao,

1164
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,180
 dao ti je predotigao na platnju,

1165
00:42:44,180 --> 00:42:45,340
 onaj koji tebe hoće ubit,

1166
00:42:45,340 --> 00:42:46,740
 sad ti imaš priliku.

1167
00:42:46,740 --> 00:42:50,160
 I Šaul se zamislio.

1168
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:54,360
 A onda ga je opekla save što je to zamislio

1169
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:57,280
 i rekao je svojima ukorio ih je,

1170
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,540
 on je pomazanik.

1171
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:04,560
 On je od gospodina.

1172
00:43:04,560 --> 00:43:07,900
 On je moj autoritet.

1173
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,600
 I otišao,

1174
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:11,500
 ocijeko mu je skut haljine.

1175
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:15,200
 I kasnije kad je Šaul izašao,

1176
00:43:15,200 --> 00:43:16,320
 David mu je pokazao.

1177
00:43:17,680 --> 00:43:19,900
 I rekao je li ja imam krivnje?

1178
00:43:19,900 --> 00:43:22,980
 Vidiš da sam te imao u svojim rukama,

1179
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:24,120
 što sam ti zlo učinio?

1180
00:43:24,120 --> 00:43:25,540
 I tu se Šaul pokajo.

1181
00:43:25,540 --> 00:43:27,140
 I rekao,

1182
00:43:27,140 --> 00:43:30,200
 ti si postupio sve to,

1183
00:43:30,200 --> 00:43:31,480
 ja sam kriv što te idem ubit.

1184
00:43:33,060 --> 00:43:35,940
 I vratio ga i postavio ga ponovno u službu,

1185
00:43:35,940 --> 00:43:38,440
 ali nakon nekog vremena opet isto stvar.

1186
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:39,120
 Zavis,

1187
00:43:39,120 --> 00:43:40,280
 taj, taj, taj, ponovno.

1188
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:41,740
 I David

1189
00:43:41,740 --> 00:43:44,760
 ga je imao još jednom

1190
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:46,160
 u rukama,

1191
00:43:46,160 --> 00:43:48,300
 kad je tvrd san pao na

1192
00:43:48,300 --> 00:43:50,400
 Šaula i njegove ljude.

1193
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:52,480
 I oni su došli,

1194
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:55,040
 po noći u njegov šator,

1195
00:43:55,040 --> 00:43:57,960
 njegov vojskovoća.

1196
00:43:58,660 --> 00:44:00,460
 Davidov prvi mu je rekao,

1197
00:44:00,460 --> 00:44:01,340
 sad ga imaš.

1198
00:44:01,340 --> 00:44:04,100
 Ali David je ostao čvrst.

1199
00:44:04,100 --> 00:44:05,480
 To je bila zadnja kušnja.

1200
00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:08,100
 A činilo se kao da mu je Bog to sve složio.

1201
00:44:08,100 --> 00:44:09,080
 Gledaj, pao je tvrd san,

1202
00:44:09,080 --> 00:44:09,980
 on je moj neprijatelj,

1203
00:44:09,980 --> 00:44:11,680
 kvari izraelski narod.

1204
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:15,480
 Ali ne, neću dići ruku na pomazenika Boga,

1205
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:16,960
 živoga, Jahve.

1206
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:20,100
 I tu je David bio obilno nagrađen.

1207
00:44:20,100 --> 00:44:21,780
 I znamo da je David

1208
00:44:21,780 --> 00:44:24,540
 najpoznatiji kralj Izraela

1209
00:44:24,540 --> 00:44:25,560
 poslije gospodina.

1210
00:44:27,380 --> 00:44:29,380
 Čovjek po srcu Božje.

1211
00:44:29,380 --> 00:44:35,060
 Tako da častit,

1212
00:44:35,060 --> 00:44:36,380
 čak i onda

1213
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:40,340
 kad duhovni autoritet nije u pravu.

1214
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:43,700
 Jer ne častimo onoga

1215
00:44:43,700 --> 00:44:45,600
 koji predstavlja taj autoritet,

1216
00:44:45,600 --> 00:44:47,300
 nego onoga koji daje autoritet,

1217
00:44:47,300 --> 00:44:47,900
 a to je Bog.

1218
00:44:47,900 --> 00:44:50,120
 Samo Krista.

1219
00:44:50,120 --> 00:44:53,600
 Sad bih prešao na drugi dio

1220
00:44:53,600 --> 00:44:54,900
 koji je malo škakljivi,

1221
00:44:54,900 --> 00:44:56,360
 to je državni voditelji.

1222
00:44:57,100 --> 00:44:59,200
 jer su Plenković i Milanović,

1223
00:44:59,200 --> 00:45:01,380
 naši političari.

1224
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:05,740
 Velika je kriza

1225
00:45:05,740 --> 00:45:10,120
 i malo gdje se može čut

1226
00:45:10,120 --> 00:45:12,180
 da će neko govorit ovako,

1227
00:45:12,180 --> 00:45:13,200
 pa čak i u crkvi.

1228
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:15,580
 Jer mi Hrvati

1229
00:45:15,580 --> 00:45:17,040
 imamo taj problem.

1230
00:45:17,040 --> 00:45:18,940
 Mi uopće ne znamo

1231
00:45:18,940 --> 00:45:20,220
 kako se časti vlast.

1232
00:45:21,060 --> 00:45:22,000
 Možda si možemo,

1233
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:24,420
 malo se možemo opravljati,

1234
00:45:24,420 --> 00:45:26,160
 jer skoro tisuću godina

1235
00:45:26,160 --> 00:45:27,660
 nismo imali svoju državu.

1236
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:29,380
 Od Zvonimira

1237
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,140
 i kogod je vladao nad nama,

1238
00:45:31,140 --> 00:45:34,080
 on nas je tlačio i kraj od nas.

1239
00:45:34,080 --> 00:45:36,700
 I nemamo to u sebi.

1240
00:45:36,700 --> 00:45:37,760
 Ne znamo častiti,

1241
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:38,480
 oni su uvijek bili

1242
00:45:38,480 --> 00:45:40,180
 kontra naroda.

1243
00:45:40,340 --> 00:45:40,960
 niko nije radio

1244
00:45:40,960 --> 00:45:41,980
 u interesu naroda.

1245
00:45:41,980 --> 00:45:49,620
 I moram vam reći

1246
00:45:49,620 --> 00:45:50,300
 da ipak

1247
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:53,260
 moramo častiti svoje državne.

1248
00:45:53,260 --> 00:45:56,200
 Čak danas ja vidim

1249
00:45:56,200 --> 00:45:57,980
 na našoj sceni

1250
00:45:57,980 --> 00:45:59,060
 političare

1251
00:45:59,060 --> 00:46:01,140
 koji se zovu katoličkim,

1252
00:46:01,140 --> 00:46:03,560
 vidim i katoličke udruge

1253
00:46:03,560 --> 00:46:05,180
 koje su aktivne u politici,

1254
00:46:05,180 --> 00:46:09,260
 koji su prvi i prednjače

1255
00:46:09,260 --> 00:46:10,240
 u kritiziranju,

1256
00:46:10,240 --> 00:46:11,800
 postavljanju,

1257
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:13,740
 koji se postavlja superiorno

1258
00:46:13,740 --> 00:46:16,080
 i malo me sram,

1259
00:46:16,080 --> 00:46:18,040
 što se zovu katolički.

1260
00:46:18,040 --> 00:46:19,900
 Jer to nije biblijski put.

1261
00:46:19,900 --> 00:46:22,060
 To nije put katoličke crkve.

1262
00:46:22,060 --> 00:46:25,820
 Rimljani 13.

1263
00:46:25,820 --> 00:46:38,560
 Svaka duša neka se podlaže vlastima

1264
00:46:38,560 --> 00:46:40,320
 nad sobom.

1265
00:46:40,320 --> 00:46:41,720
 Jer nema vlasti

1266
00:46:41,720 --> 00:46:42,440
 doli od Boga.

1267
00:46:42,440 --> 00:46:45,100
 Koje postoje

1268
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:46,680
 od Boga su postavljane.

1269
00:46:46,680 --> 00:46:49,980
 Stoga tko se suprostavlja

1270
00:46:49,980 --> 00:46:50,540
 vlasti

1271
00:46:50,540 --> 00:46:51,720
 Božjoj se

1272
00:46:51,720 --> 00:46:52,480
 odredbi

1273
00:46:52,480 --> 00:46:53,260
 protivi.

1274
00:46:53,260 --> 00:46:55,840
 Jeste svjesni što ovdje kaže?

1275
00:46:55,840 --> 00:46:57,780
 Plenković i Milanović su od Boga.

1276
00:46:59,840 --> 00:47:01,400
 oni su postavljeni od Boga.

1277
00:47:03,880 --> 00:47:04,800
 njih treba častiti.

1278
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:06,640
 Jesu li uvijek upravo?

1279
00:47:06,640 --> 00:47:06,980
 Nisu.

1280
00:47:06,980 --> 00:47:11,460
 Ali nam to ne daje pravo

1281
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,320
 da ih ne častimo.

1282
00:47:13,500 --> 00:47:14,920
 Daću vam primjer jedne zajednice.

1283
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:18,900
 Jedne zajednice koja je stagnirala tri godine.

1284
00:47:18,900 --> 00:47:27,220
 Vojitelj te zajednice više nije znao šta da učini, ali je primijetio jednu stvar.

1285
00:47:27,760 --> 00:47:32,680
 Svi članovi njegove zajednice su opasno kritizirali državnu vlast,

1286
00:47:32,680 --> 00:47:38,100
 mjesnu, ona kojim nabija poreze i mnogi nisu plaćali poreze.

1287
00:47:38,100 --> 00:47:45,900
 I on ih je oštro, ali u ljubavi, poučio o ovom što piše u Rimljanima 13, cijeli tekst, napravio predavanje.

1288
00:47:45,900 --> 00:47:53,840
 Otišo u mjesnu zajednicu i pito je tamo u općini koja je najveća potreba mjesne zajednice.

1289
00:47:53,840 --> 00:48:01,520
 Oni su mu rekli, najveća potreba je vatrogascima posebne nekakve gas maske s kojima oni vide u dimu.

1290
00:48:01,520 --> 00:48:05,800
 Jer najviše ljudi zapravo u požaru umre od dima, a ne od vatre.

1291
00:48:05,800 --> 00:48:09,340
 Uguše se i njima te maske pomažu da spašave živote.

1292
00:48:09,340 --> 00:48:11,360
 Oni se riskiraju i žrtvuju.

1293
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:15,640
 I nakon te teme koje mi je održao, rekao mi je danas skupljamo za te maske.

1294
00:48:15,640 --> 00:48:19,780
 Jedna košta 25 tisuća dolara, to je u Americi bilo.

1295
00:48:19,780 --> 00:48:21,920
 I oni su skupili za jednu masku.

1296
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:35,480
 I kad su organizirali poklon za tu ekipu, za gradsku zajednicu i sve čelnike, oni su se šokirali koliko ljudi zapravo iz vlasti došlo.

1297
00:48:36,820 --> 00:48:47,940
 I kad je voditelj, ovako po Rimljanima 13, rekao da oni ovim činom žele zahvaliti na svemu što oni rade za njih i da ih smatraju Božim slugama,

1298
00:48:49,700 --> 00:48:51,060
 ovi su bili oduševljeni.

1299
00:48:51,060 --> 00:48:56,800
 Samo to su rekli, bez ikakve kritike, bez ikakve zamolbe da se nešto napravi.

1300
00:48:56,800 --> 00:48:58,340
 Znate šta se dogodilo?

1301
00:48:58,340 --> 00:49:01,280
 Neki od tih službenika,

1302
00:49:01,280 --> 00:49:04,020
 vlasti su došli na susrete,

1303
00:49:04,020 --> 00:49:08,280
 to se pročulo i oni su postali jedna ugledna zajednica

1304
00:49:08,280 --> 00:49:14,300
 koja je sa sto članova počela organizirati konferencije za devetsto ljudi.

1305
00:49:14,300 --> 00:49:16,300
 Devetsto vjernih su imali u zajednici.

1306
00:49:16,300 --> 00:49:18,400
 I logično je, ljudi moji.

1307
00:49:18,400 --> 00:49:21,880
 Jer oni su primili nagradu

1308
00:49:21,880 --> 00:49:24,920
 jer su dali čast kome?

1309
00:49:24,920 --> 00:49:27,240
 Društvenim voditeljima.

1310
00:49:27,240 --> 00:49:30,900
 Prirodno je da je društveni voditelj čuvar,

1311
00:49:30,900 --> 00:49:34,000
 odnosno ključar vrata grada, vrata mjesta,

1312
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:37,820
 vrata neke zajednice, općine, županije.

1313
00:49:39,020 --> 00:49:42,500
 I ako se otvore ta vrata, otvaraju se vrata za sve te ljude.

1314
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:46,460
 A mi nemamo takvu kulturu.

1315
00:49:46,460 --> 00:49:48,380
 I tu kulturu treba izgrađivati.

1316
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:50,400
 Čašćena voditelja.

1317
00:49:50,400 --> 00:49:54,780
 Sad ćete me pitati,

1318
00:49:54,780 --> 00:49:58,480
 je li to isključuje da ih treba opominjati

1319
00:49:58,480 --> 00:49:59,680
 kad nešto loše rade? Ne.

1320
00:49:59,680 --> 00:50:02,240
 Ali danas toga nema, ljudi moji.

1321
00:50:02,240 --> 00:50:06,600
 Nema onog opominjanja kako smo čuli danas u Evanđelju.

1322
00:50:08,280 --> 00:50:10,500
 Ivano pominje kralja Heroda.

1323
00:50:10,500 --> 00:50:14,620
 Javno i otvoreno.

1324
00:50:14,620 --> 00:50:16,500
 Ali u ljubavi.

1325
00:50:16,500 --> 00:50:17,740
 Znate kako to znamo?

1326
00:50:17,740 --> 00:50:19,860
 Jer kaže da ga je Herod poštovao,

1327
00:50:19,860 --> 00:50:23,460
 volio ga slušat i često se našao zadivljen.

1328
00:50:26,500 --> 00:50:28,920
 To ne gasi našu proročku službu.

1329
00:50:28,920 --> 00:50:34,000
 Ali naša proročka služba se ne može odraditi u kafiću,

1330
00:50:34,000 --> 00:50:35,880
 na kavi i cigari,

1331
00:50:35,880 --> 00:50:39,500
 ili doma kad ručeš sa svojima.

1332
00:50:39,500 --> 00:50:41,340
 Ne može.

1333
00:50:41,340 --> 00:50:44,860
 Ona se mora biti izrečena u ljubavi ako si pozvan.

1334
00:50:44,860 --> 00:50:47,440
 Onome koma treba riječ poslati.

1335
00:50:47,820 --> 00:50:49,000
 Koji vam je jako dobar primjer?

1336
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:50,780
 Samuel i Šaul.

1337
00:50:50,780 --> 00:50:51,780
 Samuel prorok,

1338
00:50:51,780 --> 00:50:54,160
 kojeg je Bog podigo,

1339
00:50:54,160 --> 00:50:55,200
 kojeg je Bog volio.

1340
00:50:55,200 --> 00:50:58,640
 Kad je Šaul otvoreno

1341
00:50:58,640 --> 00:51:03,460
 i drsko,

1342
00:51:03,460 --> 00:51:06,380
 nepoštivo ono što mu je Bog rekao da napravi.

1343
00:51:06,380 --> 00:51:09,280
 Napravi kleto uništenje nad Amalećanima.

1344
00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:11,800
 On je zadržao najbolju stoku zbog naroda.

1345
00:51:14,820 --> 00:51:16,840
 Šaul dobio od gospodina proročku riječ za njega

1346
00:51:16,840 --> 00:51:19,860
 da se gospodin pokaju što ga je postavio za kralja.

1347
00:51:19,860 --> 00:51:23,740
 Odlazimo s tako proročkom, teškom riječi

1348
00:51:23,740 --> 00:51:25,760
 i znate šta poslije bude

1349
00:51:25,760 --> 00:51:28,140
 nakon što se Šaul ispričavao bezuspješno.

1350
00:51:28,140 --> 00:51:29,800
 Šaul ga moli

1351
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:32,700
 da ipak s njim dođe pred glavare.

1352
00:51:32,700 --> 00:51:35,740
 Da mu iskaze čast.

1353
00:51:35,740 --> 00:51:37,860
 I samo ide s njim.

1354
00:51:44,820 --> 00:51:48,400
 Dobar glas.

1355
00:51:48,400 --> 00:51:53,240
 Tako ćemo imati dobar glas mi, katolici.

1356
00:51:53,240 --> 00:51:55,920
 Kad poštojemo one koji su iznad nas.

1357
00:51:55,920 --> 00:52:00,260
 Ne radi nas sami da imamo neke veze, vezice.

1358
00:52:00,260 --> 00:52:03,120
 Nego da se kraljestvo Bože širi.

1359
00:52:06,240 --> 00:52:10,140
 I ovaj citat vodilja gdje Petar kaže

1360
00:52:10,140 --> 00:52:12,560
 kralja častite.

1361
00:52:12,560 --> 00:52:16,620
 Morate znat da je tad kralj bio njegov sin,

1362
00:52:16,620 --> 00:52:18,140
 Herodov sin, Heroda Gripa.

1363
00:52:18,140 --> 00:52:21,420
 I on je bio kralj koji je progonio kršćane.

1364
00:52:21,420 --> 00:52:23,460
 On je bio kralj koji je ubio Jakova,

1365
00:52:23,460 --> 00:52:24,780
 brata Ivanova.

1366
00:52:24,780 --> 00:52:29,020
 On je bio kralj koji je stavio Petra u tamnicu

1367
00:52:29,020 --> 00:52:30,320
 i htio ga pogubiti,

1368
00:52:30,320 --> 00:52:34,180
 ali su poslušni i vjerni kršćani molili.

1369
00:52:34,180 --> 00:52:37,320
 I on je bio čudesno izbavljen.

1370
00:52:37,320 --> 00:52:42,140
 Ali Bog je dosudio njemu

1371
00:52:42,140 --> 00:52:43,700
 zbog poslušnosti crkve.

1372
00:52:43,700 --> 00:52:47,520
 Nakon toga vidimo da ga Bog kažnjava

1373
00:52:47,520 --> 00:52:48,940
 i Bog se sudi s njim.

1374
00:52:48,940 --> 00:52:52,020
 Jer on održi govor.

1375
00:52:52,020 --> 00:52:53,900
 Svi kažu ovo je božanski,

1376
00:52:53,900 --> 00:52:55,720
 ovo su Božje riječi.

1377
00:52:55,720 --> 00:52:57,820
 I budući da on svom srcu nije dao

1378
00:52:57,820 --> 00:52:59,300
 hvalu Bogu za taj govor.

1379
00:52:59,300 --> 00:53:01,880
 Piše da je u trenu

1380
00:53:01,880 --> 00:53:04,620
 pao mrtav.

1381
00:53:04,620 --> 00:53:08,320
 Srvi su ga iznutra pojeli.

1382
00:53:08,320 --> 00:53:11,060
 To se dogodilo Herodu u gripi.

1383
00:53:11,060 --> 00:53:12,460
 Bog se s njima obračunava.

1384
00:53:12,460 --> 00:53:17,760
 Bog postavlja i one loše

1385
00:53:17,760 --> 00:53:18,840
 i pokvarane vladare.

1386
00:53:18,840 --> 00:53:20,840
 Na bukodonozora

1387
00:53:20,840 --> 00:53:24,080
 koji je tlačio Izraelce godinama

1388
00:53:24,080 --> 00:53:25,100
 zove

1389
00:53:25,100 --> 00:53:26,800
 pozovi moga slugu.

1390
00:53:27,820 --> 00:53:30,940
 toga moramo biti svjesni.

1391
00:53:30,940 --> 00:53:33,020
 Ali duboko u srcu,

1392
00:53:33,020 --> 00:53:34,020
 ne samo ovako izvana.

1393
00:53:34,020 --> 00:53:36,360
 U svojem djelovanju,

1394
00:53:36,360 --> 00:53:38,380
 svojim mislima,

1395
00:53:38,380 --> 00:53:39,200
 riječima,

1396
00:53:39,200 --> 00:53:40,300
 pazit.

1397
00:53:40,300 --> 00:53:41,620
 Da damo čast

1398
00:53:41,620 --> 00:53:43,300
 društvenim voditeljima.

1399
00:53:43,300 --> 00:53:47,300
 Odnosno državnim.

1400
00:53:47,300 --> 00:53:49,640
 A sad prelazimo na

1401
00:53:49,640 --> 00:53:51,300
 društvene.

1402
00:53:51,300 --> 00:53:53,460
 To su

1403
00:53:53,460 --> 00:53:55,500
 naši poslodavci, učitelji.

1404
00:53:56,420 --> 00:53:57,340
 Znate šta, iskreno,

1405
00:53:57,340 --> 00:53:59,580
 kad pričam ovako s mladima,

1406
00:53:59,580 --> 00:54:01,540
 posljedno znaših zajednica,

1407
00:54:01,540 --> 00:54:03,680
 i kad pričam, ne znam,

1408
00:54:03,680 --> 00:54:04,820
 fakultetu u školi,

1409
00:54:04,820 --> 00:54:06,860
 rijetko kad čujem dobru riječ

1410
00:54:06,860 --> 00:54:07,920
 o profesoru i učitelju.

1411
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:08,560
 Ali čujem.

1412
00:54:08,560 --> 00:54:11,500
 Ali kad se priča o poslodavcima,

1413
00:54:11,500 --> 00:54:13,700
 nisam čuo dugo jednu dobru.

1414
00:54:15,700 --> 00:54:17,620
 A šta Pavao piše?

1415
00:54:17,620 --> 00:54:19,160
 Hoću vam to pročitati.

1416
00:54:19,160 --> 00:54:24,060
 U Efežanima.

1417
00:54:26,340 --> 00:54:29,320
 Tad je još bilo legalno imat roba.

1418
00:54:29,320 --> 00:54:31,000
 On kaže, robovi,

1419
00:54:31,000 --> 00:54:33,180
 slušajte svoje zemaljske gospodare,

1420
00:54:33,180 --> 00:54:34,060
 kao Krista,

1421
00:54:34,060 --> 00:54:35,960
 sa strahom i trepetom,

1422
00:54:35,960 --> 00:54:37,460
 u jednostavnosti srca.

1423
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:40,100
 Možda nismo robovi,

1424
00:54:40,100 --> 00:54:41,840
 jer imamo pravo dati otkaz,

1425
00:54:41,840 --> 00:54:42,840
 ali ti hosam sati,

1426
00:54:42,840 --> 00:54:44,020
 kad ti radiš za poslodavca,

1427
00:54:44,020 --> 00:54:45,380
 on je tebi zemaljski gospodar.

1428
00:54:45,460 --> 00:54:47,640
 ti moraš raditi ono što on kaže,

1429
00:54:47,640 --> 00:54:48,900
 inače nećeš dobiti plaću.

1430
00:54:48,900 --> 00:54:50,800
 Ne na oko,

1431
00:54:50,800 --> 00:54:54,560
 kao oni koji se ulaguju ljudima,

1432
00:54:54,560 --> 00:54:56,020
 nego kao sluge Kristove

1433
00:54:56,020 --> 00:54:57,640
 koji izdušno vrše volju Božju.

1434
00:54:57,640 --> 00:54:59,820
 Dragovoljno služe kao gospodinu,

1435
00:54:59,820 --> 00:55:00,560
 a ne ljudima.

1436
00:55:00,560 --> 00:55:02,740
 Znajući da će svako bi on rob

1437
00:55:02,740 --> 00:55:03,500
 ili slobodnjak,

1438
00:55:03,500 --> 00:55:05,620
 učnili što dobro,

1439
00:55:05,620 --> 00:55:07,760
 zato dobiti plaću od gospodina.

1440
00:55:07,760 --> 00:55:10,140
 Služite im,

1441
00:55:10,140 --> 00:55:13,100
 slušajte ih,

1442
00:55:13,100 --> 00:55:15,300
 zemaljske gospodare,

1443
00:55:15,460 --> 00:55:16,240
 kao Krista.

1444
00:55:16,240 --> 00:55:18,740
 Možemo li se tim pohvaliti?

1445
00:55:18,740 --> 00:55:22,420
 Toga ne postoji,

1446
00:55:22,420 --> 00:55:23,500
 toga je jako malo.

1447
00:55:23,500 --> 00:55:27,000
 Ima jako dobrih i loših primjera

1448
00:55:27,000 --> 00:55:27,600
 koje sam čuo.

1449
00:55:27,600 --> 00:55:29,420
 Prvo je,

1450
00:55:29,420 --> 00:55:31,600
 htio bih vam odmah reći,

1451
00:55:31,600 --> 00:55:33,140
 nisu svi poslodavci sveci.

1452
00:55:33,140 --> 00:55:34,600
 Malo koji sve,

1453
00:55:34,600 --> 00:55:35,640
 danas posebno,

1454
00:55:35,640 --> 00:55:37,700
 kad se lovi za profitom,

1455
00:55:37,700 --> 00:55:39,320
 za osobnim koristima.

1456
00:55:39,320 --> 00:55:41,640
 Slušao sam svjedočanstvo

1457
00:55:41,640 --> 00:55:42,840
 jednog vjernika Crnca.

1458
00:55:44,460 --> 00:55:45,840
 taj vjernik Crnac je radio

1459
00:55:45,840 --> 00:55:47,600
 u kući za osiguranja.

1460
00:55:47,600 --> 00:55:51,540
 I bio je vrhunski u svom poslu.

1461
00:55:51,540 --> 00:55:53,300
 I jako dugo je proveo u toj firmi

1462
00:55:53,300 --> 00:55:54,540
 i oslobodilo se mjesto

1463
00:55:54,540 --> 00:55:56,120
 voditelja poslovanja,

1464
00:55:56,120 --> 00:55:57,340
 odmah drugi čovjek firme.

1465
00:55:57,340 --> 00:55:58,660
 I po svemu,

1466
00:55:58,660 --> 00:56:00,660
 po svakoj mogućoj pravednosti,

1467
00:56:00,660 --> 00:56:01,920
 on je trebao biti na tom mjestu.

1468
00:56:01,920 --> 00:56:02,680
 Najduže u firmi,

1469
00:56:02,680 --> 00:56:03,840
 najbolje poznaje posao,

1470
00:56:03,840 --> 00:56:05,240
 najviše je doprineo

1471
00:56:05,240 --> 00:56:06,560
 cijeloj organizaciji.

1472
00:56:06,560 --> 00:56:09,460
 Ali je bio Crnac.

1473
00:56:09,460 --> 00:56:11,800
 I direktor je zaposljio

1474
00:56:11,800 --> 00:56:13,140
 jednog bijelca na tom mjestu.

1475
00:56:13,140 --> 00:56:15,960
 Zamislite što se u njegovom srcu

1476
00:56:15,960 --> 00:56:16,720
 sve probudilo.

1477
00:56:16,720 --> 00:56:18,560
 To bi za njega značilo

1478
00:56:18,560 --> 00:56:19,380
 veća plaća,

1479
00:56:19,380 --> 00:56:20,480
 veće pogodnosti,

1480
00:56:20,480 --> 00:56:22,180
 fleksibilnije radno vrijeme.

1481
00:56:24,320 --> 00:56:25,480
 I nepravda.

1482
00:56:25,480 --> 00:56:28,940
 I on je već bio spreman

1483
00:56:28,940 --> 00:56:30,560
 kao vjernik

1484
00:56:30,560 --> 00:56:32,800
 ići tužiti svog direktora.

1485
00:56:32,800 --> 00:56:35,600
 To se kod njih moglo.

1486
00:56:35,600 --> 00:56:38,080
 I mogo je dobiti tu tužbu

1487
00:56:38,080 --> 00:56:40,980
 i moglo se presuditi njemu u korist.

1488
00:56:40,980 --> 00:56:42,400
 On je mogo dobiti veliku očtetu.

1489
00:56:42,400 --> 00:56:44,700
 Ali je

1490
00:56:44,700 --> 00:56:48,660
 posavjeto se svojim duhovnikom

1491
00:56:48,660 --> 00:56:50,560
 koji mi objasnio

1492
00:56:50,560 --> 00:56:52,040
 da mora počastiti

1493
00:56:52,040 --> 00:56:53,200
 i svog direktora

1494
00:56:53,200 --> 00:56:55,400
 i da mora počastiti

1495
00:56:55,400 --> 00:56:57,680
 i onoga koji će sad doći

1496
00:56:57,680 --> 00:56:58,780
 na tu poziciju

1497
00:56:58,780 --> 00:56:59,840
 koja će biti iznad njega.

1498
00:56:59,840 --> 00:57:02,000
 Jer je to biblijski

1499
